        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Microsoft 游戏部门裁员 1,900 人　前 Activision Blizzard 员工和 Xbox 团队受影响</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/microsoft-lays-off-1900-activision-blizzard-xbox-staff/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-lays-off-1900-activision-blizzard-xbox-staff</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/microsoft-lays-off-1900-activision-blizzard-xbox-staff/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 15:00:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Activision Blizzard]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[microsoft]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[xbox]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1217598</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>经过一番波折，Microsoft 才终于成功完成收购 Activision Blizzard 不久，最近就宣布针对游戏部门裁员，影响约 8% 员工。<br /><span id="more-1217598"></span></p><p>Microsoft 最近发出内部备忘录，表示在 Activision、Blizzard 和 King 团队加入 Microsoft 之后，认为需要精简重叠的架构进行重组，从而减省不必要的开支来专注于核心业务增长，在裁员计划之下，游戏部门包括原 Activision Blizzard 员工和 Xbox 团队之中会有 1,900 人受影响。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">I want to thank everyone who is impacted today for their meaningful contributions to their teams, to Blizzard, and to players’ lives. It’s an incredibly hard day and my energy and support will be focused on all those amazing individuals impacted – this is in no way a reflection…</p><p>&mdash; Mike Ybarra 🎄 (@Qwik) <a href="https://twitter.com/Qwik/status/1750527310493868293?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 25, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>Activision Blizzard 前总裁 Mike Ybarra 早前已经宣布收购过渡完成后将会离职，同时其前设计总监 Allen Adham 也会离职，显示团队加入 Microsoft 之后领导层也会有不少的变动，而除了人员变动外，本身 Activision Blizzard 正在开发的一个生存游戏也会取消开发，将资源重新分配给其他项目。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-lays-off-1900-activision-blizzard-xbox-staff-verge-2024-01-25/">Reuters</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/02/activision-blizzard-android-app-store/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">曾考虑自设 Android 游戏商店   Activision Blizzard 嫌赚钱不多放弃计划</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/microsoft-lays-off-1900-activision-blizzard-xbox-staff/game-channel/">Microsoft 游戏部门裁员 1,900 人　前 Activision Blizzard 员工和 Xbox 团队受影响</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
